notes:
**1st Power: Aim for something that helps earn cash quickly.**

- [Medimaster](item_a04e1041-01c1-46ed-801e-d0590003e9b6) 
Pick if: Enemy tank is Zarya or Orisa (easy headshots from the front); your team has Zarya or Junker Queen (easy healing headshots from behind). Only take if your aim is good.

Avoid if: Your team has Reinhardt, Orisa, or D.Va (unreliable healing headshots from behind).

- [Medicinal Missiles](item_30eeab6c-4a1e-4a16-b9dd-e83d633caa40) 
Pick if: The other support is Mercy or Ana (you can outpace their single-target healing for more cash).

- [Pulsar Plus](item_4795ae1f-580d-47ec-a01d-0933cba56212) 
Pick if: The map preview shows good torpedo maps like Throne of Anubis, Colosseo, or Redwood Dam (especially Redwood), where you can use Torpedo effectively

- [Blink Boosts](item_9bac3119-781b-4dc0-94fa-9c293c02dc90) 
Pick if: Enemy tank is Rein, D.Va, or Orisa; enemy DPS includes Genji or Cassidy (helps escape high-threat situations, like Orisa's ult).

---

**Must Pick:**
- [Armored Vest](item_358361e2-59be-4c81-b221-8a87f37809e6): Consistent and valuable.

**Pick 2 of the Following 3 Options:**
- [Compensator](item_2a354f80-610c-4661-9bdd-8960ae1a60b0): A full burst is 90 damage (12 bullets x 7.5), healing is 72 (12 x 6). This adds ~4.5 extra damage or ~3.6 extra healing per burst.
- [Weapon Grease](item_961ae72f-434f-406b-a89b-ab8efec806bf): Increases rate of fire from 1.29 bursts/sec to ~1.35 bursts/sec. Reload speed (1.8s) remains unchanged.
- [Power Playbook](item_6d8803cf-baa7-46ee-af91-51e7f2301418): Pick only if the map favors torpedoes or you took Medicinal Missiles as your first power.

notes:
**Case 1: You’re Dying Too Much (Dove or Sniped):**
If divers (Genji, Reaper, Moira) or hitscan (Cassidy, Ashe) are focusing you, prioritize survival.

Must Buys:
- [Armored Vest](item_358361e2-59be-4c81-b221-8a87f37809e6)
- [First Aid Kit](item_0172eaaa-1902-44a3-b989-d12f0f7301da) 
- [Winning Attitude](item_8714087c-c078-4619-a2ef-327bc6edaa69) 

This provides +75 bonus HP, plus ~25 base health from cash scaling, effectively ~100 extra HP, bringing baseline HP to around 325 (a 44% increase).

**Pick One Situational Item:**
- [Ironclad Exhaust Ports](item_2d085fa5-ace6-4fab-9323-b7a06268bcd0): Synergizes with [Blink Boosts](item_9bac3119-781b-4dc0-94fa-9c293c02dc90). Timed well, 4 dashes + ring + torpedoes can create 150 overhealth. Great for enemy with damage overtime.
- [Lock-On Shield](item_220287f8-1dc5-4a6c-9e86-c14cf970b689): Synergizes with [Pulsar Plus](item_4795ae1f-580d-47ec-a01d-0933cba56212). Two torpedoes grant 75 overhealth baseline.
- [Reinforced Titanium](item_8ebaa7db-aedf-48ed-adc1-318cb46a3214): Adds +25 shield and reduces ability damage by 15%. Good against Soldier rockets, Ashe dynamite, Rein fire strike, or another torpedo Juno.
- [Crusader Hydraulics](item_b64cee07-ca32-405d-987e-868b415bbc09): Take against weapon damage heavy heroes.
- [Iron Eyes](item_f16d03a7-f20e-4a1d-a1f6-55863e163c03): Take against headshot heavy heroes (Cassidy).

This results in +30 AP. This loadout helps secure kills or save allies during burst windows.

**2nd Power: This choice is situational, based on the match's progression.**

If you took [Blink Boosts](item_9bac3119-781b-4dc0-94fa-9c293c02dc90) or [Medimaster](item_a04e1041-01c1-46ed-801e-d0590003e9b6) first:
- Consider [Pulsar Plus](item_4795ae1f-580d-47ec-a01d-0933cba56212) if you're not under pressure and landing crits safely, to boost cash gain.
- Consider [Medicinal Missiles](item_30eeab6c-4a1e-4a16-b9dd-e83d633caa40) if your team is struggling to stay alive.

If you took [Pulsar Plus](item_4795ae1f-580d-47ec-a01d-0933cba56212) or [Medicinal Missiles](item_30eeab6c-4a1e-4a16-b9dd-e83d633caa40):
- Take the opposite of these two together, as they synergize well for high healing and cash generation.

[Stinger](item_e9d0d530-d620-4e74-a34d-38cdebfeb9a4):
- Useful against long-range enemies (DoT ignores range drop-off and armor, delays enemy self-regen). You can spread this to multiple enemy at long range to get cash fast.
- Strong synergy with [Mark of the Kitsune](item_09a53e39-25aa-4f66-ba51-bedbc543a1eb) (item providing +25 AP to next shot after ability). With 30 AP, [Medimaster](item_a04e1041-01c1-46ed-801e-d0590003e9b6), and [Stinger](item_e9d0d530-d620-4e74-a34d-38cdebfeb9a4), a combo can yield significant burst: Torpedo (110) + Stinger (13) + [Mark of the Kitsune](item_09a53e39-25aa-4f66-ba51-bedbc543a1eb) bonus (32) + Primary (135, all headshots) ≈ 290 damage. Even with no head shots, ~245 damage is possible.
